1 set forth in SECTION 1 of this resolution, shall be submitted to the
2 people of Oklahoma for their approval or rejection as and in the
3 manner provided by law.
4 SECTION 4. The President Pro Tempore of the Senate shall,
5 immediately after the passage of this resolution, prepare and file
6 one copy thereof, including the Ballot Title set forth in SECTION 2
7 hereof, with the Secretary of State and one copy with the Attorney
8 General.
9
